des:
Use Alexa to operate your device.
You can simply ask Alexa to turn your air purifier on or off. No need to go to the switch to adjust your air purifier, just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.
After connecting Alexa to your Airfree products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our Airfree app from Android or ios app market;
(2) Register an Airfree account on our Airfree app;
(3) You need to have some smart Airfree devices with you;
(4) Configure these devices in our Airfree app and change the appropriate name for your devices that will be used in Skill Airfree (eg purifier, lamp and fan);
(5) Download the Amazon “Alexa” app from Android, ios or Amazon app market;
(6) Configure the Echo with the “Alexa” app;
(7) Search Skill Airfree from the Skills category of the “Alexa” application;
(8) Click Activate Airfree Skill, and you will be redirected to Airfree login page, follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(9) Now all the setup is complete. You can enjoy voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the purifier.”
“Alexa, turn off the purifier.”
“Alexa, turn on the lamp.”
“Alexa, set the lamp to 50.”
“Alexa, turn on the fan.”
